                        <interp inst="t18500408-name-630" type="given" value="FRANCES"></interp>FRANCES MITCHELL</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I was talking to Mrs. Brockliffe on the Monday evening, and heard the strange footstep.</p>
